{
  "_comment": [
    "IAM permissions policy for role agrisync-snapshot-dev.",
    "spec: voice-diary-e2e-2026-05-17 (snapshot prereqs)",
    "runbook: _COFOUNDER/runbooks/prod-snapshot.md §1+§3+§5",
    "",
    "Scope (founder lock):",
    "  WRITE-only to agrisync-snapshots-dev bucket (PutObject + GetObject for verify; NO Delete)",
    "  READ-only inventory on agrisync-raw-dev (List + GetObjectVersions)",
    "  READ-only inventory on agrisync-voice-retained-dev (List + GetObjectVersions)",
    "  Encrypt + Decrypt + GenerateDataKey on alias/agrisync-snapshots-dev",
    "  GetSecretValue on agrisync/snapshot/pg-dev (the secret comes later; permission ready)",
    "",
    "Notably: NO s3:DeleteObject / s3:DeleteObjectVersion anywhere. Combined with bucket",
    "versioning, this enforces append-only on the verification log AND the snapshot files",
    "themselves — only the bucket lifecycle policy (a bucket-owner action) can age them out.",
    "",
    "The script writes per-snapshot files and appends to _verification-log.jsonl by",
    "READ-then-PUT-with-versioning. Old versions of the log are preserved forever (until",
    "the lifecycle NoncurrentVersionExpiration ages them out at 591 days)."
  ],
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Sid": "SnapshotBucketWriteAndReadForVerify",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "s3:PutObject",
        "s3:GetObject",
        "s3:GetObjectVersion",
        "s3:ListBucket",
        "s3:ListBucketVersions",
        "s3:GetBucketLocation"
      ],
      "Resource": [
        "arn:aws:s3:::agrisync-snapshots-dev",
        "arn:aws:s3:::agrisync-snapshots-dev/*"
      ]
    },
    {
      "Sid": "RawBlobInventoryReadOnly",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "s3:ListBucket",
        "s3:ListBucketVersions",
        "s3:GetBucketVersioning",
        "s3:GetBucketLocation"
      ],
      "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::agrisync-raw-dev"
    },
    {
      "Sid": "RetainedVoiceInventoryReadOnly",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "s3:ListBucket",
        "s3:ListBucketVersions",
        "s3:GetBucketVersioning",
        "s3:GetBucketLocation"
      ],
      "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::agrisync-voice-retained-dev"
    },
    {
      "Sid": "KmsForSnapshotKey",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "kms:Encrypt",
        "kms:Decrypt",
        "kms:GenerateDataKey",
        "kms:DescribeKey"
      ],
      "Resource": "*",
      "Condition": {
        "ForAnyValue:StringEquals": {
          "kms:ResourceAliases": "alias/agrisync-snapshots-dev"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "Sid": "PgSecretReadOnly",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "secretsmanager:GetSecretValue",
        "secretsmanager:DescribeSecret"
      ],
      "Resource": "arn:aws:secretsmanager:ap-south-1:951921970996:secret:agrisync/snapshot/pg-dev-*"
    }
  ]
}
